						 <p>So this <a href="http://www.scp-wiki.net/forum/t-2116184" target="_blank">Anomalous Item Tale Challenge</a> seems to be the popular thing lately, so here's my contribution.</p> <p>Was inspired after reading <a href="http://www.scp-wiki.net/forum/t-4275202/tum-tum-tum-tum-tum-tum-tum-tum-tum-tum" target="_blank">Tufto's</a> tale.</p> <p>I realise that MaliceAF has already written a <a href="http://www.scp-wiki.net/time-after-time">tale</a> for this challenge on this exact item, but I checked with them first and they are cool with me writing one on it too.</p> <p>Thanks to Tufto, MaliceAF and ARD for checking the draft.</p> <p>Oh, you can read more of my nonsense <a href="http://www.scp-wiki.net/mortos-author-page">here.</a></p> 
				 	]]>
